    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Wicka</h1>
        <p class="last"> Wicka was once a living, breathing woman, but she put her soul into a wax figurine so she could live forever.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="450"src="media/gifs/whip_wand2.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Health and Mana</h1>
        <p>Wicka uses both health and mana to power her spells.</p>
        <p class="last">Her mana cannot exceed her health, but replinishes over time. Her health does not.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="30"src="media/gifs/mana_health_bar2.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Enchanted Candles</h1>
        <p>If she can touch them, Wicka can melt and assimilate the candles into her body, healing any damage she's sustained.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="387"src="media/gifs/telekinesis_brick_riding2.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Wicka's Flame</h1>
        <p>The flame on Wicka's head can be sent out, to illuminate the subject of her attention, locking the camera to that enemy.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="387"src="media/gifs/melt_self1.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Whip Wand</h1>
        <p>Whip Wand turns Wicka's wand into a whip.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="397"src="media/gifs/whip_wand1.gif" alt="">
        <h3>*This spell requires no mana or health to cast.</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Melt Self</h1>
        <p>Turning her body into molten wax, Wicka sinks below the stone floor to evade her enemies.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="387"src="media/gifs/melt_self2.gif" alt="">
        <h3>*Caution: this spell uses health to cast.</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Freeze Ray</h1>
        <p>Freeze enemies in their tracks, for a time.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="387"src="media/gifs/freeze_ray1.gif" alt="">
        <h3>*This spell uses mana.</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Telekinesis</h1>
        <p>Wicka can lift the heavy stones from the floor with her magic and toss them at her enemies.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="387"src="media/gifs/telekinesis3.gif" alt="">
        <h3>*This spell uses mana.</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Telekinesis, Brick-Riding</h1>
        <p>Using Telekinesis, Wicka can lift the stones from the floor and walk on them.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='600' height="338"src="media/gifs/telekinesis_brick_riding.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Immolate</h1>
        <p>Turn Wicka's flame into a raging inferno.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="387"src="media/gifs/immolate.gif" alt="">
        <h3>*Caution: this spell uses health to cast.</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Immolate, Melt Ice</h1>
        <p>Bricks frozen by Freeze Ray cannot be lifted by Telekinesis. Use Immolate to melt the ice.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="387"src="media/gifs/immolate_melt_ice.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Cursed Grimoires</h1>
        <p>Some spell books are cursed and attack any who come too close.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="387"src="media/gifs/book1.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h1>Monsters</h1>
        <p>Wherever spellcasters are, monsters are too. They come in a variety of forms, but are always hostile. Some say these monsters are representations of the spellcaster's own demons made real by her magic.</p>
